newcomerScoutTitle: Become the Smile Newcomer of the Year 2025!

children.text: We’re kicking off the next round – the big scouting for the Newcomer Creator of the Year 2025 is starting!
We’re looking for the most creative, authentic, and versatile social media talent.
The Top 3 will take the stage at the Swiss Influence Awards and compete for the prestigious Smile Swiss Influence Newcomer Award.
🏆 A role in the new Smile Insurance TV commercial
🎓 Access to the Swiss Creator Academy (valued at CHF 1,799.-)
💫 Respect, fame & recognition in the industry!
